  "notes": "Goldenrod City is the largest city in Johto. Warps to Underground use GOLDENROD_UNDERGROUND_SWITCH_ROOM_ENTRANCES as an intermediate map. The Radio Tower Takeover is a major late-game story event (after Mahogany Gym). The Move Tutor is a post-Elite-4 event. Map dimensions per pokecrystal: 20x18 blocks (40x36 tiles). Object positions in tile coordinates (1 block = 2 tiles)."
